headline.main: BOARD OF HEALTH.; ADJOURNMENT WITHOUT TRANSACTION OF BUSINESS.

docs.snippet: At the meeting of the Board of Aldermen, last evening, a resolution was adopted directing the Street Commissioner to proceed at once with the laying out of Mount Morris-square.

docs.lead_paragraph: For whatever color of truth can be found in the charge brought against the "institutions" of the United States by Earl GREY, that the great mass of the people never know who their member is in any legislative body, the City of New-York, as now administered, is mainly responsible.
